short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Best JDM Cars from the web

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
We share all the cool jdm motors from around the internet and hopefully build a database of JDM cars that are getting rare. We find ourselves constantly looking at jdm cars for sale that we will never be able to afford but just like looking and hoping some day.

We have had a number of cool JDM cars previously but age and commitment meant that we had to sell them unfortunately. We have also imported many of our own JDM cars.
